\page\n\pard\ql\f1\fs30\sb180\sa180\keepn\cf1\brdrb\brdrs\brdrw12\brdrcf2\brsp80\b 1  Executive summary\b0\par
\pard\ql\f0\fs22\sb0\sa160 The work is divided into six stages. The ordering is deliberate: first prove the numerical contracts and address mapping; then prove that the remainder can affect the forward path; then prove that it can learn with an intentionally expensive reference optimiser; only then build the memory-clean custom optimiser.\par
\pard\sb120\sa160\li180\ri180\brdrt\brdrs\brdrw10\brdrcf2\brdrl\brdrs\brdrw28\brdrcf2\brdrb\brdrs\brdrw10\brdrcf2\brdrr\brdrs\brdrw10\brdrcf2\shading100\cbpat3\f0\fs22 \b Critical path\b0\line Exact decoding -> exact materialised-weight addressing -> exact gradient decomposition -> R1 reference proof -> R2 memory-clean optimiser.\par\n\trowd\trgaph90\trleft0\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrl\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrb\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrr\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clpadl90\clpadr90\clpadt70\clpadb70\clcbpat3\cellx700\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrl\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrb\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrr\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clpadl90\clpadr90\clpadt70\clpadb70\clcbpat3\cellx4600\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrl\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrb\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrr\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clpadl90\clpadr90\clpadt70\clpadb70\clcbpat3\cellx8500\pard\intbl\f0\fs18\sb0\sa0 \b\cf1 Stage\b0\cf0\cell\pard\intbl\f0\fs18\sb0\sa0 \b\cf1 Primary outcome\b0\cf0\cell\pard\intbl\f0\fs18\sb0\sa0 \b\cf1 Decision at exit\b0\cf0\cell\row\n\trowd\trgaph90\trleft0\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrl\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrb\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrr\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clpadl90\clpadr90\clpadt70\clpadb70\cellx700\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrl\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrb\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrr\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clpadl90\clpadr90\clpadt70\clpadb70\cellx4600\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrl\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrb\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrr\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clpadl90\clpadr90\clpadt70\clpadb70\cellx8500\pard\intbl\f0\fs18\sb0\sa0 0\cell\pard\intbl\f0\fs18\sb0\sa0 Stable contracts, exact decoder, exact projector and offline diagnostic.\cell\pard\intbl\f0\fs18\sb0\sa0 Proceed only when the mathematics and indexing are proven.\cell\row\n\trowd\trgaph90\trleft0\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrl\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrb\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrr\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clpadl90\clpadr90\clpadt70\clpadb70\clcbpat4\cellx700\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrl\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrb\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrr\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clpadl90\clpadr90\clpadt70\clpadb70\clcbpat4\cellx4600\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrl\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrb\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrr\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clpadl90\clpadr90\clpadt70\clpadb70\clcbpat4\cellx8500\pard\intbl\f0\fs18\sb0\sa0 1\cell\pard\intbl\f0\fs18\sb0\sa0 Forward-only int8 remainder path.\cell\pard\intbl\f0\fs18\sb0\sa0 Proceed only when zero equivalence and single-position addressing are proven.\cell\row\n\trowd\trgaph90\trleft0\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrl\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrb\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrr\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clpadl90\clpadr90\clpadt70\clpadb70\cellx700\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrl\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrb\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrr\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clpadl90\clpadr90\clpadt70\clpadb70\cellx4600\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrl\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrb\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrr\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clpadl90\clpadr90\clpadt70\clpadb70\cellx8500\pard\intbl\f0\fs18\sb0\sa0 2\cell\pard\intbl\f0\fs18\sb0\sa0 One-backprop gradient routing and R1 reference optimiser.\cell\pard\intbl\f0\fs18\sb0\sa0 Proceed only when the remainder demonstrably learns.\cell\row\n\trowd\trgaph90\trleft0\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrl\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrb\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrr\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clpadl90\clpadr90\clpadt70\clpadb70\clcbpat4\cellx700\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrl\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrb\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrr\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clpadl90\clpadr90\clpadt70\clpadb70\clcbpat4\cellx4600\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrl\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrb\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrr\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clpadl90\clpadr90\clpadt70\clpadb70\clcbpat4\cellx8500\pard\intbl\f0\fs18\sb0\sa0 3\cell\pard\intbl\f0\fs18\sb0\sa0 R2 factored-RMS stochastic integer optimiser.\cell\pard\intbl\f0\fs18\sb0\sa0 Proceed only when it trains, resumes and satisfies the state-memory contract.\cell\row\n\trowd\trgaph90\trleft0\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrl\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrb\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrr\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clpadl90\clpadr90\clpadt70\clpadb70\cellx700\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrl\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrb\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrr\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clpadl90\clpadr90\clpadt70\clpadb70\cellx4600\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrl\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrb\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrr\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clpadl90\clpadr90\clpadt70\clpadb70\cellx8500\pard\intbl\f0\fs18\sb0\sa0 4\cell\pard\intbl\f0\fs18\sb0\sa0 Matched scientific sweep.\cell\pard\intbl\f0\fs18\sb0\sa0 Proceed, revise the optimiser, or stop.\cell\row\n\trowd\trgaph90\trleft0\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrl\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrb\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrr\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clpadl90\clpadr90\clpadt70\clpadb70\clcbpat4\cellx700\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrl\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrb\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrr\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clpadl90\clpadr90\clpadt70\clpadb70\clcbpat4\cellx4600\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrl\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrb\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clbrdrr\brdrs\brdrw8\brdrcf4\clpadl90\clpadr90\clpadt70\clpadb70\clcbpat4\cellx8500\pard\intbl\f0\fs18\sb0\sa0 5\cell\pard\intbl\f0\fs18\sb0\sa0 Packed storage and streamed backward if required.\cell\pard\intbl\f0\fs18\sb0\sa0 Complete the intended memory architecture.\cell\row\n\pard\sa140\par\n\pard\sb120\sa160\li180\ri180\brdrt\brdrs\brdrw10\brdrcf2\brdrl\brdrs\brdrw28\brdrcf2\brdrb\brdrs\brdrw10\brdrcf2\brdrr\brdrs\brdrw10\brdrcf2\shading100\cbpat7\f0\fs22 \b Central caution\b0\line Stage 3 is expected to require substantial work. It is not an AdamW subclass with a few lines changed. It is a separate optimiser whose parameter is a bounded signed integer code, whose incoming gradient is continuous, and whose persistent state must remain much smaller than a dense weight matrix.\par\n\page\n\pard\ql\f1\fs30\sb180\sa180\keepn\cf1\brdrb\brdrs\brdrw12\brdrcf2\brsp80\b 2  Implementation principles\b0\par
\pard\f0\fs22\li540\fi-270\sb0\sa95\bullet\tab Preserve the existing path. When remainder_mode is off, no remainder storage, hook, optimiser state or altered arithmetic may be created.\par
\pard\f0\fs22\li540\fi-270\sb0\sa95\bullet\tab Commit a stage-specific test plan before writing production code for that stage.\par
\pard\f0\fs22\li540\fi-270\sb0\sa95\bullet\tab Separate representational proof from memory engineering. R1 may be expensive; R2 may not.\par
\pard\f0\fs22\li540\fi-270\sb0\sa95\bullet\tab Use one canonical matrix coordinate system: the final two-dimensional (out_features, in_features) matrix consumed by the linear operation.\par
\pard\f0\fs22\li540\fi-270\sb0\sa95\bullet\tab Do not apply coefficient gradients twice. Hook mode returns the projected matrix gradient to existing autograd; explicit coefficient gradients are diagnostic until streamed autograd is introduced.\par
\pard\f0\fs22\li540\fi-270\sb0\sa95\bullet\tab Unsupported configurations and checkpoint mismatches must fail before training starts.\par
\pard\f0\fs22\li540\fi-270\sb0\sa95\bullet\tab Measure persistent memory and peak transient memory separately.\par
\pard\f0\fs22\li540\fi-270\sb0\sa95\bullet\tab Remain on remainder_architecture_enhancement unless a different branch is explicitly requested.\par
\pard\ql\f1\fs25\sb160\sa100\keepn\cf1\b 2.1  Source-change discipline\b0\par
\pard\ql\f0\fs22\sb0\sa160 Existing nanoGPT and THOG2 lines are not to be deleted. Superseded lines are to be commented out where practical. All new or changed THOG2 code must use the established trailing or block THOG markers.\par
\pard\ql\f1\fs25\sb160\sa100\keepn\cf1\b 2.2  No second training backend\b0\par
\pard\ql\f0\fs22\sb0\sa160 The remainder implementation must plug into the existing model construction, materialisation, training loop, checkpoint, resume/fork, telemetry and wrapper paths. It must not create a parallel trainer.\par
\page\n\pard\ql\f1\fs30\sb180\sa180\keepn\cf1\brdrb\brdrs\brdrw12\brdrcf2\brsp80\b 3  Object model and terminology\b0\par
\pard\ql\f0\fs22\sb0\sa160 The architecture has five persistent object classes. The table below states plainly what each is, why it exists, and when it is used.\par
