\pard\f0\fs22\li540\fi-360\sb0\sa105 1.\tab Convert the rejected weight gradient into a gradient measured in remainder-code units.\par
\pard\f0\fs22\li540\fi-360\sb0\sa105 2.\tab Update row and column squared-gradient averages.\par
\pard\f0\fs22\li540\fi-360\sb0\sa105 3.\tab Use those factors to normalise the code-space gradient.\par
\pard\f0\fs22\li540\fi-360\sb0\sa105 4.\tab Clip the normalised update by RMS.\par
\pard\f0\fs22\li540\fi-360\sb0\sa105 5.\tab Convert the desired fractional code movement into an up, hold or down decision by seeded stochastic rounding.\par
\pard\f0\fs22\li540\fi-360\sb0\sa105 6.\tab Apply the integer step and clamp it to the signed bit-width range.\par
